From: Folia Compatibility Patch
Subject: [PATCH 0003] Effect-Engine: Migrate ExecutionTask to SchedulerUtils and update AdvancedWeapon attributes

AE PATCH REASON: Core effect engine uses synchronous waits and incompatible attributes
AE PATCH FIX: Migrate ExecutionTask to SchedulerUtils and update AdvancedWeapon attributes
AE PATCH RISK: HIGH
AE PATCH EXCLUDES: net/advancedplugins/ae/impl/effects/effects/actions/execution/ExecutionTask.class, net/advancedplugins/ae/impl/effects/effects/actions/execution/ExecutionTask$*.class, net/advancedplugins/ae/features/weapons/AdvancedWeapon.class, net/advancedplugins/ae/features/weapons/AdvancedWeapon$*.class

---
